{
  "stem": "2916.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the plan was-- and the order came down from Eisenhower-- to find this train-- oh yes, so I must say that the reason we were evacuated from Muehldorf and two more camps nearby who-- the inmates all worked in a cement factory.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Through these people who knew how to work with cement were being shipped to Otztal to complete the Alpine Fortress.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was like a last minute, desperate effort by Hitler to prolong the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so this is where our train was heading in Austria.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These inmates were going to build and complete this fortress.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is the reason why the Americans not only happened on our train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were looking for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Documents show that they found us at a point called Poing, P-O-I-N-G, where the train was attacked.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the order was, completely destroy the train, not only the train, but the people in it because they were considering that if the train is destroyed, maybe it will be shipped by trucks to complete the work.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the aim was to kill everyone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, to me, this was such a shocking news that I didn't want to believe it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Westebe, Peter Westebe in Seeshaupt, who was doing some of the research, promised me to send me xeroxed documents, a xeroxed copy of all the documents in which he found this information.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if this is true, then this is a fantastic story of a last minute annihilation by our liberators.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Once we were liberated in Seeshaupt-- by the way, I don't want to believe it until I see those documents.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I haven't received them yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I spoke to him last Wednesday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I phoned him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he said that he's almost ready to send me the entire package with pictures and documents.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
